data.description: Welcome to 1025 Indiana St. this welcoming home features beautiful original woodwork and updates throughout. This move-in ready home hosts a cozy living room with a gorgeous fireplace (electric), beautiful dining room and large kitchen! Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and a recently updated bathroom. 1025 Indiana features a large front porch and a flat fenced in back yard with privacy fence and shed. Beyond the privacy fence you will find a concrete pad and enough space for four off street parking spots. This home has had many updates within the last several years. Per seller some updates include new flooring, freshly painted interior, kitchen and bathroom remodel within the last 2 years, furnace replaced 3 years ago, hot water tank replaced 2 years ago, a/c replaced 5 years ago and new windows and roof in 2013 as well as updated electric. This home is ready for it's new family! Bring your belongings and move right in! Schedule your showings today!
